{"_id":"57cd9147067a8fd63bba07bc","groupId":100,"createDate":"2016-09-05T15:37:43.364Z","createUserId":"55e5c6995a761f8a46b34399","ownerType":1,"ownerId":"57c00930fd5c737a358f566f","against":false,"threadId":null,"parentId":null,"editDate":"2016-09-05T15:37:43.364Z","editUserId":"55e5c6995a761f8a46b34399","references":"<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heroes%27_Cemetery#cite_note-Libingan7-8\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heroes%27_Cemetery#cite_note-Libingan7-8</a><br></p>","title":"Libingan ng mga Bayani Interment policy","content":"<p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">According to Armed Forces of the Philippines (AFP) Regulation G 161-373, the following persons are entitled to interment at Heroes' Cemetery:<sup id=\"cite_ref-Libingan3_5-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heroes%27_Cemetery#cite_note-Libingan3-5\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">[5]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Libingan7_8-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heroes%27_Cemetery#cite_note-Libingan7-8\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">[8]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Libingan8_9-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heroes%27_Cemetery#cite_note-Libingan8-9\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">[9]</a></sup></p><ul style=\"margin: 0.3em 0px 0px 1.6em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml%20version%3D%221.0%22%20encoding%3D%22UTF-8%22%3F%3E%0A%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20version%3D%221.1%22%20width%3D%225%22%20height%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Ccircle%20cx%3D%222.5%22%20cy%3D%229.5%22%20r%3D%222.5%22%20fill%3D%22%2300528c%22%2F%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E%0A&quot;); color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philippine_Medal_of_Valor\" title=\"Philippine Medal of Valor\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Medal of Valor</a>&nbsp;awardees</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\">Presidents or Commanders-in-Chief, AFP</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\">The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Secretary_of_National_Defense_(Philippines)\" title=\"Secretary of National Defense (Philippines)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">secretaries of National Defense</a></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\">AFP Chiefs of Staff</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\">General/Flag Officers</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\">Active and retired military personnel of the AFP</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\">Former AFP members who laterally entered/joined the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philippine_National_Police\" title=\"Philippine National Police\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Philippine National Police</a>&nbsp;(PNP) and the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philippine_Coast_Guard\" title=\"Philippine Coast Guard\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Philippine Coast Guard</a>&nbsp;(PCG)</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\">Veterans of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philippine_Revolution\" title=\"Philippine Revolution\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Philippine Revolution</a>&nbsp;of 1896, the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/First_World_War\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"First World War\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">First</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Second_World_War\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Second World War\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Second World Wars</a>, as well as recognized guerrillas</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\">Government dignitaries, statesmen, national artists and other deceased persons whose interment has been approved by the commander-in-chief, Congress or the Secretary of National Defense, and</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\">Former Presidents, Secretaries of National Defense, widows of former Presidents, Secretaries of National Defense and Chiefs of Staff</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\">National Artists and National Scientists of the Philippines<sup id=\"cite_ref-Libingan9_10-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heroes%27_Cemetery#cite_note-Libingan9-10\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">[10]</a></sup></li></ul><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">However, the same regulation also prohibits “personnel who were dishonorably separated/ reverted/ discharged from the service and personnel who were convicted by final judgment of an offense involving moral turpitude” from interment at the Heroes' Cemetery.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Libingan3_5-2\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heroes%27_Cemetery#cite_note-Libingan3-5\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">[5]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Libingan7_8-2\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heroes%27_Cemetery#cite_note-Libingan7-8\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">[8]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Libingan8_9-2\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heroes%27_Cemetery#cite_note-Libingan8-9\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">[9]</a></sup></p>"}